description:
This is a 36 minute workout called 'Yoga For Weight Loss  |  Healthy Energy Flow  |  Yoga With Adriene' from the channel Yoga With Adriene.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Yoga For Weight Loss, Healthy Energy Flow guides you to the mat to cultivate the healthy flow of energy you need to explore your body and create a sustainable practice. 

Trim, tone and build lean muscle mass with attention on alignment, action, and sensation. 

Want to feel your best this Spring and Summer? Commit to this practice and you will want to return to the mat again and again. 
Keep returning to the mat and you will feel and see results. 

Let me know how it goes down below!

Namaste. 

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

Our Yoga For Weight Loss series is a set of full-length yoga workout videos designed to burn fat, workout your core and strengthen and lengthen your body. Check out the full playlist here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLui6Eyny-Uzx2jQYA8MS73ND2kUMHyII8
